Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.79,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:17.73,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地變得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:23.14,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,背後彷彿有你的腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:30.09,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,追趕了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:41.20,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我頻頻回頭看著你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:51.30,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,新戀情的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.41,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,是兩人在不知不覺中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:07.19,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,展開看不見的愛的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:15.36,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永遠不願分離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:24.61,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓我只愛你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨看起來真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是約會喔，約會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天，我跟學姊見面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有告訴千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也對不起你的老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能躺在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我心裏很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人是千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於初戀的人\N已經是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我能一直看到這個笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的錢包掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}#04 冬美學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏，這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會，不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！是海豹耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，還有海豚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢包掉了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為看不到海豹\N已經死心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，那不是煩惱海豹的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你把全部的錢\N都放在我這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你不曉得\N把錢包放到哪裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是我的錯囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過，阿修\N我真的玩得好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定還能再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，來拍張照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還沒一起拍過照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了照片的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得會因此就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我還在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看著真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能藉由你證明我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我能感覺到\N我真的存在於這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我相信\N我不是孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過，今天真的運氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有接到緊急出擊的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實，我把呼叫器放在家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是我第一次約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被任何人打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個壞女孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不是個壞女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是天天都有戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定真有這種日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有人不約會的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在普通的高中女生\N每個人都在約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊，所以你沒有做錯事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天全世界一定都很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這個城鎮一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裏是我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上根本沒有和平了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在比這個更大的城市\N都會很輕易的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在瞬間就被毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實千瀨的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的低到令人鼻酸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在到底\N有多少屬於「人」的部份呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的頸部依然如此纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的髮香依然令人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還是被找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去拿錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是來拿錢包而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也到了能讓女人\N枕腕而睡的年紀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點感動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的，學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會做出讓千瀨傷心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是她男朋友\N為什麼總是讓她哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都決定當她的男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都決定相戀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我無法保護千瀨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨她又沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我也沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到千瀨寂寞的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨現在\N可能也在某個地方哭泣著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…好燙\N你幹嘛買熱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買錯了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換成千瀨\N你可能會笑著原諒她，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，快點跟千瀨做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會輕鬆很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個都太笨拙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛這麼雞婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實，我覺得我很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨今天又請假了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她從小身體就很虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還曾經在東京的醫院\N住院了好幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又笨笨的\N沒有什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應過她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會一直保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論什麼事我都會幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要她打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課的時候你也呆呆的看著\N千瀨請假缺席的空位子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正這張送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那張八百年前的照片\N別帶在身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這張好好帶著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的部份塗掉沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦，就這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果啊，那時候她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能給我一點水喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，我看還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真正的千瀨妹妹耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好佩服你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那一仗你打得好棒喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的好強喔，千瀨妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個\N怎麼可以這樣對長官說話！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的部下失禮了，很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鐵小隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，我不是叫你\N不要叫我阿鐵小隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷達還是無法發揮作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干擾波太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ECCM也沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法估計還剩多少敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要命，這不就等於\N是在一百年前打仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才千瀨中隊長大發神威\N把敵人全滅了不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在謙虛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中村！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有敵人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且數量不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可能已經被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會再去解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她吃的藥好像有點不尋常…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實剛才戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意放走了很多敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的敵人實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過用力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕一個不小心\N這個城市也會被我「那個」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿淳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由佳利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛，好痛喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為千瀨妹妹說\N他有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長得怎麼樣？比我帥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，別發出那種\N丟人現眼的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實他也談不上帥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像阿鐵小隊長這種人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你罵「白癡」的時候\N跟他有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從我變成終極武器之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成為別人眼中的不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裏的人什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常逃學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜還會偷跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家對我都已經死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本懶得管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿修現在還會罵我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他動不動就會罵我「傻瓜」\N或是「你這個笨蛋」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是個武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明殺了那麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他還會罵我「笨蛋」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道你是終極武器嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道，札幌空襲的時候\N被他看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每當阿修罵我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有一瞬間\N我都會覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我還是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我還有資格活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為你的奮戰是有很意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那場戰鬥我差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧你奮戰救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奮戰的…意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對啊！\N要不是你，我也早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近漸漸地可以\N控制自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一上戰場\N馬上就會失去意識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後身體就自己動起來\N變得很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子國外不是有個小鎮\N憑空消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意識的話\N我會覺得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過最近習慣了\N只要忍耐一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望多少能幫別人一點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼話啊，千瀨妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幫了很多人的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然這國家早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了，不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說這些有的沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的沒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你也不要想太多\N專心作戰就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人已經來了，在上空盤旋著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭，他們是衝著我來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經被鎖定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全體撒退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說內地被炸得很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比札幌慘很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是望著這麼美麗的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對無法想像那種景象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個城市真的很和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裏是我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼其它的地方很慘\N這只是謠言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要信以為真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我還是希望這個城市\N能夠永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奮戰的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有意義的話\N我想保護
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護爸爸、媽媽、弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城市所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我希望靠我的力量\N盡可能保護這個星球更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來\N阿修會不會稍微誇獎我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來，從那天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我爽約的那天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直處於的這種尷尬狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能稍微回復到以前那樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣，我要再加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微再出一點力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要努力奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先發制人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓阿修誇獎我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表現得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你把我殺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經受不了這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是個武器\N竟然還以為能保護人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望心愛的人永遠不變\N是愚蠢的想法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是因為我太年輕的關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是千瀨也還只是個高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才十七歲，個子小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:43.46,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:50.45,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,難以入眠的夜裏總不停的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:59.63,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺中黎明已悄悄到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.98,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼想聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:13.15,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:20.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,對你的思念越來越強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.09,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,淚水奪眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:30.26,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:36.50,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍無法忘懷你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.38,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:46.91,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:52.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，為什麼要忍耐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還只是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在談戀愛的普通高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多跟我聊一些吧，千瀨
